query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `inspection_environments` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `inspection_id` int NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `caixilho_code` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `caixilho_type` text NOT NULL,
  `quantity` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `planta_file_key` varchar(500),
  `planta_file_url` varchar(1000),
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  CONSTRAINT `inspection_environments_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  CONSTRAINT `inspection_environments_inspection_id_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`inspection_id`) REFERENCES `inspections`(`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE
);
